== G-Code Reception & Parsing ==
UART -> GCODE : "G90G1X100Y25F1000S200M3\\n"
GCODE -> GCODE : Tokenize â†’ ["G90", "G1X100Y25F1000", "S200", "M3"]
GCODE -> GCODE : Store in gcodeCommandQueue (16-command buffer)
